# LogMirrorRadar - Log Frequency & Pattern Detector

LogMirrorRadar summarizes recurring log entries and reveals patterns, ideal for error investigation and monitoring.

## Features
- Finds top repeated lines  
- Custom keyword scanning  
- Visual log summaries  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LogMirrorRadar.git
cd 23_LogMirrorRadar
python analyze.py
